### 我的作品列表
GET {{host}}:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/{{version}}/work/myList?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 我的作品列表：模糊搜 title
GET {{host}}:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/{{version}}/work/myList?page=1&pageSize=10&title=dream&status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 作品详情（必须登录；非作者必须 isPublic=true）
GET {{host}}:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/{{version}}/work/detail?id=6
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 编辑作品
POST {{host}}:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/{{version}}/work/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "id": 6,
  "title": "new title",
  "desc": "new desc",
  "coverImg": "https://example.com/cover.png",
  "content": {
    "components": [
      {
        "LText": 123
      }
    ],
    "props": {
      "color": "red"
    }
  }
}

### 发布作品
POST {{host}}:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/{{version}}/work/publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "id": 9
}

